an1.11:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel purrong ally mia-ang ghain yorga-ang kaart mokin nunn-o-luck purrong ung ghain maaman. Nunn-o-luck purrong ung ghain maaman mia-ang ghain yorga-ang kaart.
an1.12:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally yunga-ang irabin penin youqual kaart-warra, ka, nginder irabin penign-ang malaj mogin battiti. Nginder noon-da yakka barra penin nunn-o-luck gaign battiti, kaart-warra irabin, nginder irabin malaj good-jeer malaj.”
an1.13:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally yunga-ang irabin penin monogming, ka, nginder irabin penign-ang, malaj mogin yoo-ly, bidibaba nunn-o-luck da-ban. Nginder noon-da malaj good-jeer malaj.”
an1.14:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally yunga-ang irabin penin yabra kaart, ka, nginder irabin penign-ang, malaj mogin yabbra kaart. Nginder yabbra kaart malaj good-jeer malaj.”
an1.15:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally yunga-ang irabin penin cumbarng , ka, nginder irabin penign-ang malaj mogin ki-an-kartaga. Nginder noon-da yakka barra penin nunn-o-luck gaign ki-an-kartaga, cumbarng malaj good-jeer malaj.”
an1.16:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al youqual quairty goor-do, ka, nginder irabin penign-ang malaj mogin penign-ang bang-al mogin meanyaper. Nginder noon-da yakka meeal bang-al moorditj, goor-do bang-al.”
an1.17:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al youqual kaart-warra , ka, nginder irabin mogin bang-al mogin moorditj woon-ya koort. Nginder noon-da kaart-warra bang-al moorditj woon-ya koort mogin.”
an1.18:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al youqual kaart-warra , ka, nginder irabin mogin bang-al mogin koort woon-ya moorditj. Nginder noon-da kaart-warra bang-al koort woon-ya moorditj mogin.”
an1.19:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al yabra kaart , ka, nginder irabin penign bang-al mogin woon-ya kaart. Nginder woon-ya kaart, yabra kaart bang-al.”
an1.19:1.2: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al cumbarng , ka, nginder irabin penign bang-al mogin moorditj kaart. Nginder moorditj kaart, cumbarng bang-al.”
an1.20:1.1: “Kwabba-winyarn-ang, nad-joo arn-dinyung ki-an meeal ghain ghaingel gaign ally bang-al cumbarng , ka, nginder irabin penign bang-al mogin moorditj kaart. Nginder moorditj kaart, cumbarng bang-al.”
